Interface ProtocolHandlerChain

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractProtocolHandlerChain, LMTPProtocolHandlerChain, POP3ProtocolHandlerChain, ProtocolHandlerChainImpl, SMTPProtocolHandlerChain

    public interface ProtocolHandlerChain
    Chain which can be used to get all Handlers for a given Class.
